title: The.Dark.Side.of.Oz
description:
Read .nfo file

This is my first torrent.  I am aware that this file might be around already.

The original flac is the remastered version of the dark side of the moon, and I decided to encode it as an mp3 @ 320 kbps.

So, it might be lossy, but its the least.

Just run it as normal on vlc or whatever player you like best, keep in mind the original audio track fades out.

After the album ends, you'll notice the audio fades in again.  So, that means that this won't loop, and why would it...
I don't believe there is any major sync after the first run.  So if you like, enjoy the rest of the movie, its trippy.
THC will always enhance the experience.

Seed and enjoy.

XOXO

ralfalfa
